restaurantList.name: Grill London (Kaunas, PLC Mega)
restaurantList.description: „Grill London” is a chain of grill restaurants that visitors love because of its exceptional and responsible take on food quality. All of its steaks are grilled in unique ceramic grills using ecological fuels.

reviews.comment: Tasty burgers, but had to wait a long line.
Didn't have fried rice, a bit disappointed.
Food didn’t meet my expectations, but it was fine. But the customer experience was flawless!
Good burgers, good price

restaurantList.name: Jurgis ir Drakonas
restaurantList.description: Jurgis ir Drakonas make pizza for the real heroes. Real heroes understand the best quality. Our authenitic Neapolitan tradition pizza are made from real Italian 00 flour. Tomatoes grown under the hot Italian sun are ripe and rich, and Italian fior di latte mozzarella melts in your mouth.

reviews.comment: Cosy outside seating, tasty food. Recommended for everyone who’s looking for nice dinner both inside or outside.
Nice place, a lot of natural food, exclusive pizza. Ice cream which you can get only in this restaurant. Good place for children.
Ok pizza, good beer. Environment is better for family than for business traveler attempting to relax over dinner. Lots of kids.
Nice pizza, but not the best I had. Friendly staff, reasonably priced menu. Was very quiet when we visited.
Hated it.
Most awesome pizza I ever had!

restaurantList.name: Mamma Pizza
restaurantList.description: Small, but very cozy place in the center of Kaunas, very tasty food with vegetarian options, vegan too. Super friendly staff.

reviews.comment: One of The best Pizza in town. Good fresh juice. Family friendly and quite nice music.
Good, but nothing special.
We ordered two pizzas. Both were almost cold when served (it was not busy time). Beer and cider one the other hand were warm on a day of 30 degrees celsius.
The best pizza`s in Kaunas. Very delicious, quality ingredients, very kind and good service and affordable prices. Must visit.

restaurantList.name: MOMO Grill Kaunas
restaurantList.description: Chef and owner of MOMO GRILL is widely known for his international experience, but what he’s actually FEELING can only be revealed after taking a bite, a spoonful or otherwise sampling his cooking. Knowledge AND feelings. Seasons AND emotions. Flavour AND memories. Sometimes it’s so simple that it can even be complicated.

reviews.comment: Very tasty, good service, nice ambience, good location. 10 points ;) Mimosas, soups, beef, coffee, ice cream.
Nice place in downtown of Kaunas. Tasty food. Cosy accomodation. Perfect dishes. Highly reccomend for friends, business and family.
I don't really like meat.
My favorite restaurant in Kaunas for brunch, lunch, dinner or sweet dessert!
Great service, very good food. Every time it is worth to come back.
I love good steak and this is the best one i can get in Kaunas city.
I like the food there. The meat is so nicely grilled!
Best brunch in town! Egg Benedicts and English breakfast was really very delicious! Best wishes, can't wait to come back!

restaurantList.name: Restoranas Siesta
restaurantList.description: Delicious food, cozy atmosphere, family friendly
restaurantList.address: Pakrantes g. 4 Vareikonys, Kauno r., Kaunas

reviews.comment: Beautiful restaurant in the centre of Lithuania next to highway Klaipėda-Kaunas. Delicious food, nice choice, good local and imported drinks.
Too fancy for my taste.
Excellent place, excellent food, perfect service, nice view. I will come back next time and save some space for desert.

restaurantList.name: Restoranas DIA
restaurantList.description: We are ready to arrange you an unforgettable celebration, restaurant staff will take care about all the smolest details: decorate the hall, arrange musicians, agree the celebration menu with the customer, will make all kinds of world cuisine dishes.

reviews.comment: We visited with friends. Great service, very tasty food, cozy environment. The prices are quite high but the quality is good.
Soup was ok, reminded me of a ragu that had been transformed into a soup. Nothing special but ok.
One of the goals during our trip to Kaunas was to visit Dia. The restaurant has been listed in top 30 best restaurants in Lithuania and despite the fact, I did not hear that much buzz around it.
Best food in town, always!
Good choice for tasty meals and good service, nice interior. The place, where I'd like to come back again.
Very good quality and well presented.
Best dining experience in Kaunas

restaurantList.name: Agave
restaurantList.description: An exceptional mexican restaurant.

reviews.comment: Best Mexican place in Kaunas for sure. Appetizers, main course, dessert, all are on the high level.
We had a pleasant experience.

restaurantList.name: Moksha
restaurantList.description: Moksha is small restaurant serving pescatarian (fish & vegan) pan-asian food with a healthy twist. Majority of the food we serve is vegan. We make non traditional kimchis, kombuchas, lemonades, vegan ice-creams and vegan cakes free from added sugar.

reviews.comment: I would never usually consider going to a vegan/vegetarian restaurant but now I will because this place was so good!
Wonderful place!
Best place for environmentaly-conscious people in Kaunas!
Amazing food. Freshly prepared.

restaurantList.name: Avilys
restaurantList.description: To enjoy the beer made in restaurant’s cellar’s brewery. Avilys produce LIVE, unfiltered, unpasteurized beer. Our brand is beer with Lithuanian honey. During the beer tour and tasting we‘ll introduce you with all the specifics of AVILYS beer making. We’ll show you the inside of the brewery too.

reviews.comment: Went twice in a week, and would go again.

We enjoyed our meal here. The vaulted basement is quite atmospheric. The fried bread with cheese starter was a meal in itself. The food was very good, along with the service. Tried the beer of course.

restaurantList.name: Katpedele
restaurantList.description: Traditional Lithuanian cuisine - experience the most popular national meals, discover new tastes! The interior and the atmosphere is created to resemble unique old village style.

reviews.comment: Very tasty food, nice place, good service, tasty coctails.
Great and nice place, delicious Lithuanian food and good atmosphere.
Didn't really like the food here.
Nice place for family dinner.
Perfect, friendly and fast service, delicious Lithuanian food.

restaurantList.name: Sushi Masters
restaurantList.description: A great suhi place.

reviews.comment: Taste is perfect, but prices are very high and portions too small for this price.

restaurantList.name: Talutti - Fresh and Tasty
restaurantList.description: Nothing can be better than eating good pancakes.

reviews.comment: Cozy and nice place to have a brunch :) Tasty and fresh food, a lot of different options in the menu, prices not so high as well.
Good prices, great food.
I’m a local, I can say this is my favourite restaurant in town! Very reasonably priced, big portions, delicious food and just a great atmosphere!

restaurantList.name: ieti
restaurantList.description: Relax and enjoy old town.

reviews.comment: Almost all other reviews about this restaurant praise it very highly indeed. And they are quite correct!
Very cosy and nice place to eat.
I liked the interior.
The combination of flavours is inspired.
Had a great lunch here today. Interesting food with Lithuanian seasonal products.

restaurantList.name: Pas Stanley
restaurantList.description: Welcome to our house! We are humble and honoured for your stay at our place – a place which, we hope, will give you a warm and friendly experience and where you want to return to!

reviews.comment: Delicious homemade lemonade.
A nice relaxed place just off the old town square. Nice decor and layout, kind of a hybrid between a traditional restaurant and a bar.

restaurantList.name: Lithuanian Pub Entry
restaurantList.description: Full plates. Reasonable prices. Good vibes only. Come and see!

reviews.comment: Best chicken wings in town, quite big drinks assortiment. Good music.

restaurantList.name: Casa Della Pasta, pizzeria - restaurant
restaurantList.description: A story based on sacrifice, hard work and energy… Fabio Manconi started life with few privileges in his home town in Italy. Working in a family restaurant from a very young age, after school he waited for the right moment to get his first experiences abroad… From London, Sydney and Hong Kong, following his heart, he arrived in Kaunas, where he settled down and decided to pursue his dream. A dream called Casa della pasta.

restaurantList.name: Vista Puode
restaurantList.description: Which side of a chicken has the most feathers?

reviews.comment: Nice place to eat. Food is nothing special, but it's good.
Just the average food for higher than average prices. I would not recommend this for traditional lithuanian cousine.
We booked a table for celebration, but no one told us that we will be able to order dishes just from the lunch meniu, that involves 4 dishes...
Nice modern-folk restaurant.

restaurantList.name: Hop Doc Gastropub
restaurantList.description: HOP DOC GASTROPUB - brand new addition to Kaunas Old Town. Located few steps from a main Vilnius street, we serve you modern interior, more than 100 kinds of beers, full bar & grill. Lunch specials from 12:00 till 15:00 on work days. Fresh oysters come in every Friday. Kitchen is open till 23:00 on weekdays and till 24:00 on weekends. We recommend You to book in advance.

reviews.comment: Brilliant food and tasty beer.
Very tasty burgers. Cosy atmosphere just a few steps away from main old town street. Great place to eat and take few beers.

restaurantList.name: Al Cantuccio
restaurantList.description: A family place.

reviews.comment: Food was delicious. Staff efficient and well mannered.
Gelato and iced coffee was very delicious.
This is the top place in Kaunas to eat. Very nice inner yard with helpful staff. Very nice selection of pasta and tasty salads. We will definitely come back again.
One of my favorite restaurants.

restaurantList.name: ManGi
restaurantList.description: Bar, fast food, street food

reviews.comment: Best hot dogs in the Universe.
Very yummy, filling and interesting hotdogs. Friendly staff. Offering vegan sausages!
